DarkGlass Customization
###

DarkGlass can be customized in a number of ways:

   * [DarkGlass Configuration] deals with basic configuration.
   * [DarkGlass Organisation] gives an overview of the files and URLs used by DarkGlass.
   * [DarkGlass Templates] discusses templates, which are used to generate HTML pages, and can be used as @\$include@ files.
   * [DarkGlass Macros] can be added or modified.
   * [DarkGlass Security] discusses how to password-protect content and DarkGlass functions.